---
description: Applies to Expo, Expo Router, React Native, and NativeWind work
globs:
  - "app/**/*.tsx"
  - "components/**/*.tsx"
  - "src/**/*.ts"
  - "src/**/*.tsx"
  - "app.json"
  - "package.json"
  - "babel.config.*"
  - "metro.config.*"
  - "tailwind.config.*"
---

Before writing Expo code, read the exact Expo SDK 56 docs at `https://docs.expo.dev/versions/v56.0.0/`.

Rules:
- Use Expo Router file-based navigation.
- Keep bottom tabs named Feed, Browse, and Account.
- Keep non-tab screens aligned with `docs/USER_FLOWS.md`.
- Use TypeScript for product, rating, auth, and API code.
- Use NativeWind once configured, following current version docs.
- Do not assume older Expo or Expo Router behavior.
